## Category

### Get all ingredients
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ingredients

### Get all ingredients by recipeId
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ingredients/recipe?recipeId=asdf

### Get category by id or name
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ingredients/breakfast

### Create a category
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ingredients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 51cc0e81-4dcb-43f2-8a3d-ce77c99ac562

{
    "name": "Chili",
    "imageUrl": ""
}

### Update a category
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ingredients/6d33560a-093b-4713-8dfc-049ba978d4d1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 51cc0e81-4dcb-43f2-8a3d-ce77c99ac562

{
    "name": "eggs",
    "imageUrl": ""
}

### Delete a category
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ingredients/c971ff94-6b0c-4db0-a6c6-5a6da15dbceb
Authorization: Bearer 51cc0e81-4dcb-43f2-8a3d-ce77c99ac562